title				The Perl Pit

name				PerlPit
headline			The Perl language and accessories
description
	The Perl Pit collection of Perl packages. This pack contains Perl 5.10.0, AutoConf 2.61, AutoMake 1.9.6, Net::SSLeay 1.30, XML::Parser 2.36 and IntlTool 0.37.1. They are needed for building Syllable from source code and for some other packages and uses.

modules
	programming/languages/perl-5.10.0
;	Enlightenment needs at least 2.67:
;	programming/AutoConfigure-2.68
;	BinaryUtilities 2.20 insists on 2.64:
;	programming/AutoConfigure-2.64
;	Versions higher than 2.61 cause warnings on SDL 1.2.13:
;	BinaryUtilities 2.19(.1) insists on 2.59:
	programming/AutoConfigure-2.59
;	Enlightenment needs at least 1.11.1:
;	programming/AutoMake-1.11.3
;	GrUB doesn't work with 1.10+:
	programming/AutoMake-1.9.6
;	For ancient packages:
;	programming/autoconf-2.13
;	programming/automake-1.4-p6
	programming/LibraryTool-2.2.6b
	programming/net-ssleay-1.30
;	Linux links this dynamically into XML-Parser:
;	file/expat-2.0.0
	programming/xml-parser-2.36
	programming/IntlTool-0.40.6
